OL,7,FA woman whose cousin was killed by an
OL,8,Fex-partner in 2017 has said the safety
OL,9,Fof women and girls in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fhas not improved, despite it being
OL,11,Fnearly a decade since her murder.
OL,13,FMarcella Leonard, who is an
OL,14,Findependent social worker, said: "The
OL,15,Fsad reality is that since my cousin
OL,16,FConcepta Leonard was murdered in 2017,
OL,17,FI genuinely do not feel that I can sit
OL,18,Fhere and say that things have improved.
