OL,7,FThe Justice Minister Naomi Long said:
OL,8,F"What we're trying to do is find ways
OL,9,Fwe can work together to improve
OL,10,Flegislation to keep pace with the
OL,11,Fchanging face of abuse, but also then
OL,12,Fto try and change the culture and
OL,13,Fattitudes in society on which much of
OL,14,Fthis abuse and violence and and so on
OL,15,Fis predicated.
OL,17,F"That's a wider cultural piece which
OL,18,Fwe're doing as an Executive, so I
OL,19,Fthink it has to be both strong robust
OL,20,Flegislation and then this cultural
OL,21,Fpiece of work that we're doing.
